{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-a-css-linear-gradient-to-create-a-striped-element","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Koristite CSS `repeating-linear-gradient()` za kreiranje elementa sa prugama","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>repeating-linear-gradient()</code> funkcija je vrlo slična <code>linear-gradient()</code> sa glavnom razlikom da ponavlja definisani uzorak linije. <code>repeating-linear-gradient()</code> prihvata različite tipove vrednosti, ali za jednostavnost, koristićete vrednosti ugla i boja u ovom izazovu.</p>\n<p>Vrednost ugla je smer linije. Stope boja su kao vrednosti širine koje specificiraju gde se promene dešavaju, i daju se u procentima ili broju piksela.</p>\n<p>U primeru prikazanom u editoru koda, linija počinje sa bojom <code>yellow</code> na pikselu 0 koja se meša sa drugom bojom <code>blue</code> na udaljenosti od 40 piksela od početka. Pošto je sledeća stopa boje takođe na pikselu 40, linija se odmah menja na treću boju <code>green</code>, koja se sama meša sa vrednošću četvrte boje <code>red</code> na udaljenosti od 80 piksela od početka linije.</p>\n<p>Za ovaj primer, korisno je zamisliti stope boja kao parove gde se svake dve boje mešaju zajedno.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">0px [yellow -- blend -- blue] 40px [green -- blend -- red] 80px\n</code></pre>\n<p>Kada je svaki par stopa boje ista boja, mešanje se ne vidi jer je između iste boje, praćeno oštrim prelazom na sledeću boju, tako da dobijate prugaste linije.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ad7","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Kreirajte prugaste linije promenom <code>repeating-linear-gradient()</code> koristeći ugao linije od <code>45deg</code>, zatim postavite prve dve stope boja na <code>yellow</code>, i poslednje dve stope boja na <code>black</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/c6bmQh2","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301072,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-a-css-linear-gradient-to-create-a-striped-element"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n\n  div{\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    width: 70%;\n    height: 400px;\n    margin:  50 auto;\n    background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n      90deg,\n      yellow 0px,\n      blue 40px,\n      green 40px,\n      red 80px\n    );\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n<div></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ugao <code>repeating-linear-gradient()</code> treba da bude 45deg.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/background:\\s*?repeating-linear-gradient\\(\\s*?45deg/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Ugao <code>repeating-linear-gradient()</code> ne treba da bude 90deg ponovo</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /90deg/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Stopa boje na pikselu 0 treba da bude <code>yellow</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /yellow\\s+?0(px)?/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Prva stopa boje na pikselu 40 treba da bude <code>yellow</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /yellow\\s+?40px/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Druga stopa boje na pikselu 40 treba da bude <code>black</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /yellow\\s+?40px,\\s*?black\\s+?40px/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Poslednja stopa boje na pikselu 80 treba da bude <code>black</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /black\\s+?80px/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"use-a-css-linear-gradient-to-create-a-striped-element","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-texture-by-adding-a-subtle-pattern-as-a-background-image","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-gradual-css-linear-gradient","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ad7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-a-css-linear-gradient-to-create-a-striped-element"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}